"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Yesterday, Layer 0 protocol [#Polkadot](https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/?keywords=polkadot\\\\&highlightedUpdateUrns=urn%3Ali%3Aactivity%3A6861194346834866176) announced community participation for selecting their brand identity\\n\\nThe participation involved voting on select brand assets, with all votes verifiable [#onchain](https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/?keywords=onchain\\\\&highlightedUpdateUrns=urn%3Ali%3Aactivity%3A6861194346834866176)\\n\\nThe experience was not only exhilarating but thinking back the implication of this kind of direct voting for any major company/protocol decision allows them to take user feedback directly while making the users feel like part of the company … and all this is verifiable on-chain\\n\\nImagine if an actual government-policy based voting process happened this way … the use cases are endless,\\n\\n... from voting on HR policies within the company, selecting a new UX for a new app from the community at large, or voting on a national level policy if vaccinations are required for entry into the workplace\\n\\n2020s is going to be the decade of [#DAO](https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/?keywords=dao\\\\&highlightedUpdateUrns=urn%3Ali%3Aactivity%3A6861194346834866176) - Community based organizations\\n\\nFor those interested in how the Polkadot brand identity community-based voting happened, can check the link in the comments!\\n\",\"timestamp\":1642498631,\"title\":\"I just voted to select a logo for a $50 Billion #crypto network … and it was glorious\"},\"digest\":\"IJd0l9nGge-OJGLLZ6ZBl3YcYaZ17VM8TiDgJpo27gk\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xF41DF18b77bec4e196Ecf0178820313F9Fca3562\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"9MDTNFKkmPt6C40sVJhdzb51qYUjH7pg1dj_3mO4pF8\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"7qf62ZqRAbEAYWPawgfq4oYkqHbt4oD0egU7ASP7p-8\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"4ptRsqmBXta6GyhcYpXB5wh28UKxHkklZo28l7s76Kv1jcdN7bQSJRPHzRjvKa6yRfBIlaiGGETyNYaY7F4A_w\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xfca35987db28220465f949e8414d396e911f842c8caa46dbdad7fad0118798ab7d26b8f7967ca9be532786093ace73c092ed916e94d8da872148d1a00a92891c1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"9MDTNFKkmPt6C40sVJhdzb51qYUjH7pg1dj_3mO4pF8\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"7qf62ZqRAbEAYWPawgfq4oYkqHbt4oD0egU7ASP7p-8\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"IJd0l9nGge-OJGLLZ6ZBl3YcYaZ17VM8TiDgJpo27gk\"}"